1. Define the Roles First

You mentioned two internal wallets:

Bank (World Bank wallet)

Treasury

These must have different economic functions, otherwise the system becomes chaotic.

Bank (Operational Liquidity)

Purpose:

pay players

pay AI spending

pay mining rewards

fund gameplay economy

This wallet is active circulation.

Treasury (Strategic Reserve)

Purpose:

future liquidity pools

exchange listings

emergency liquidity

marketing / partnerships

long-term reserves

This wallet should be mostly untouched.

