instant sell

8. Dynamic Resource Value

Prices should be player driven, not fixed.

Example:

iron price = 1–3 D3X
copper = 5–10 D3X
lithium = 20–50 D3X

If AI agents buy resources, they create natural demand.

9. AI Economic Interaction

Your AI factions (Gemini / Rainclaude) should periodically buy resources.

Example spending loop:

AI wallet → purchase metals
↓
metals used to build drones
↓
drones destroyed
↓
tokens burned

This creates a closed economic loop.

10. Example Complete Flow

Player session:

1. player mines mountain
2. obtains 20 iron
3. lists iron on market
4. AI buys iron
5. player receives 40 D3X
6. player upgrades drone
7. upgrade burns 10 D3X

Token movement:

AI → player → burn

This stabilizes supply.

11. Recommended Initial Parameters
    Parameter Value
    Mining time 30–60 sec
    Energy cost 5
    Market fee 3%
    Burn 1%
    Treasury 2%
    Final Principle

Players should extract materials, not tokens.

Resources → Market → D3X → Crafting/Burn

This architecture prevents the economic collapse that occurred in games like Axie Infinity.
